name: 21Shares XRP ETP
description_en: The product tracks the value of the cryptocurrency Ripple (XRP). The ETN's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 2.50% p.a.. The 21Shares XRP ETP is the largest ETN that tracks the Ripple (XRP) index. The ETN replicates the performance of the underlying index with a collateralised debt obligation which is backed by physical holdings of the cryptocurrency. The 21Shares XRP ETP is a large ETN with 704m Euro assets under management. The ETN was launched on 21 June 2019 and is domiciled in Switzerland. Show more Show less
description_cs: Produkt sleduje hodnotu zvlnění kryptoměny (XRP).ETN TER (celkový poměr nákladů) činí 2,50% P.A .. 21Shares XRP ETP je největší ETN, který sleduje index zvlnění (XRP).ETN replikuje výkon podkladového indexu s zajištěným dluhovým závazkem, který je podporován fyzickými drženími kryptoměny.ETP 21Shares XRP je velká ETN s správou aktiv 704 milionů EUR.ETN byl spuštěn 21. června 2019 a má bydliště ve Švýcarsku.Ukázat více show méně

name: 21Shares Bitcoin Ethereum Core ETP
description_en: The 21Shares Bitcoin Ethereum index tracks the performance of the cryptocurrencies Bitcoin and Ether, which are weighted by market capitalisation in the index. The ETN's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.49% p.a.. The 21Shares Bitcoin Ethereum Core ETP is the only ETN that tracks the 21Shares Bitcoin Ethereum index. The ETN replicates the performance of the underlying index with a collateralised debt obligation which is backed by physical holdings of the cryptocurrency. The 21Shares Bitcoin Ethereum Core ETP is a small ETN with 36m Euro assets under management. The ETN was launched on 4 October 2019 and is domiciled in Switzerland. Show more Show less
